"Specifies an optional limit on the distance from the start point to the "
"network layer. If the point is further from the network than this distance "
"an error will be raised. If not set, the point will be snapped to the "
"nearest point on the network layer, regardless of how far away from the "
"network it actually is."
msgstr ""
